column3: “I LOVE this strain... its perfect to get me through a day of school where i can think clearly amd communicate with my professors... yet i can THINK without distractions and concentrate on what im doing. It puts me in a very happy and content mood and i can be in a crowd without freaking out. One of my top daytime strains”

“Pretty awesome strain. Definitely one of my new favorites. tryke grew the batch I have and i love it. it's one of those very few strains you can smoke to start your day, throughout your day, and to end your night. 5 stars”
